    <p>When editing content in <uicontrol>Text</uicontrol> mode, the following actions (in regards
      to inserting, opening, or comparing files) are available in the <menucascade>
        <uicontrol>Document</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>File</uicontrol>
      </menucascade> menu:<dl>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol>Insert File</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Inserts the content of the file with the specified file path into the current
            document, at the current position of the cursor.</dd>
